Title: Relates to requirements for licensure of certain mental health practitioners and providing such mental health practitioners authority to give diagnosis
Summary: Relates to requirements for licensure of mental health counselors and marriage and family therapists and providing mental health counselors and marriage and family therapists authority to give diagnosis.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to requirements for licensure of certain mental health practitioners and providing certain mental health practitioners authority to give diagnosis
